            "title": "穩定幣商美掛牌 港概念股猛炒",
            "description": "<p id=\"date\">2025年6月5日</p>\n<p class=\"info\">\t\n</p>\n    <h1 id=\"article-title\" class=\"sub_ex_article-title\">穩定幣商美掛牌 港概念股猛炒<br>    \n   \n    </h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2025/06/05/4103454_d1b5068701e121003998ac051ac3f4a5.png\" title=\"\" class=\"thickbox\"><img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2025/06/05/4103454_d1b5068701e121003998ac051ac3f4a5_620.png\" border=\"0\"></a></p>\n<span class='enlargeImg'><a href=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2025/06/05/4103454_d1b5068701e121003998ac051ac3f4a5.png\" title=\"\" class=\"thickbox\"><img src='https://static.hkej.com/hkej/ejweb/enlarge.gif' align='absmiddle' />放大圖片</a> / <a href=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2025/06/05/4103454_d1b5068701e121003998ac051ac3f4a5.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">顯示原圖</a></span>\n<p></p>\n全球最大穩定幣發行商之一Circle Internet（上市編號CRCL），將於美國時間周四（5日）在紐約交易所正式掛牌，是全球首次有穩定幣發行商在交易所上市，連同本港兩周前立法通過《穩定幣條例草案》，本港多隻穩定幣概念股連日偷步炒上，Circle Internet投資者之一光大控股（00165）昨...\n<p>（節錄）</p>",
            "link": "https://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/headline/article/4103454/%E7%A9%A9%E5%AE%9A%E5%B9%A3%E5%95%86%E7%BE%8E%E6%8E%9B%E7%89%8C+%E6%B8%AF%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E8%82%A1%E7%8C%9B%E7%82%92",
